      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST TOO GOOD (6) goes very well this trip starting 15 times for five wins and five minors. Hit the frame latest (17.64) when third at this track in a Grade 5/6. Looks suited and should go close. SWEETIE PIE (2) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 300m (17.56). Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Can do much better this time. CHASING THE ACE (1) out of the placings in a Grade 5 last time, colliding with another runner and finishing a 18 length eighth over 300m at this track. Has two wins from Box 1. Has the ability and can atone with the right run. BETTER HALF (8) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
